                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col text-center">
                            <h2>What is Pre-settlement?</h2>
                            <p><strong>Pre-settlement</strong> funding is a financial tool available to people pursuing legal recourse in certain circumstances. Specifically, it is available to anyone seeking compensation for physical injuries and related losses stemming from an accident or incident caused by someone else. Because the funding is provided based on the strength of your legal claim, you can only take advantage of this opportunity before your case is resolved. You can use the money to cover unanticipated or day-to-day expenses. Pre-settlement funding is not provided to finance your legal claim.</p>
                            <p>At Oasis Financial we can help by providing a safe, risk-free payment based on what your case is worth. You simply agree to repay the original amount plus charges once your case is successfully resolved. If someone’s carelessness caused your injury and you’re bringing a claim, you can contact us to learn if you qualify for pre-settlement funding. You can also read about our application process and learn more about our pre-settlement funding program below.</p>
