                                <div class="pt-3">
                                    <p><strong>What happens if I get pre-settlement funding from Oasis Financial, but I later discover it is not enough?<br /> </strong><br /> Believe it or not, this is fairly common. It often happens when a case drags on longer than anticipated. We strongly suggest our customers apply for only what they absolutely need to prevent a financial crisis. But if you are genuinely struggling while your case is pending, we will always entertain secondary requests for funding.</p>
